trans_title: 肖恩·麦克劳林: 万福玛利亚
introduction: Sean McLoughlin's bark and bite are in full effect in his stand-up special, Hail Mary. Debuted at the Top Secret Comedy Club during Edinburgh Fringe 2018 and recorded in 2019, Sean elegantly weaves a thread of wit, humor & hope throughout the dystopian framework he expertly builds throughout the hour. Not to be missed!
